<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        *{
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        html, body{
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: aliceblue;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            color: black;
        }
        .nav{
            height: 80px;
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: white;
        }
        .left{
            width: 50%;
            height: 100%;
            margin-left: 25px;
            color: black;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .right{
            width: 50%;
            height: 100%;
            color: grey;
            font-weight: 500;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            gap: 12px;
            justify-content: end;
            align-items: center;
            margin-right: 25px;
        }
        .content{
            height: calc(100% - 80px);
            background-color: white;
            width: 100%;
            color: black;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .heading{
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .title{
            color: black;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 100px;
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
        }
        span{
            font-style: italic;
            font-weight: 200;
            color: blue;
        }
        .subtitle{
            font-size: 20px;
            margin: 10px;
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            color: grey;
        }
        .btn{
            background-color: black;
            color: white;
            height: 40px;
            width: 80px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            border-radius: 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .temp{
            background-color: transparent;
            border: none;
            outline: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="nav">
        <div class="left">Logo</div>
        <div class="right">
            <p>Home</p>
            <p>About</p>
            <p>Contact</p>
            <form action="/logout" method="POST">
                <button class="temp" type="submit">
                    <p class="btn">Log out</p>
                </button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <div class="heading">
            <p class="title">Welcome, <span><%= username %></span></p>
            <p class="subtitle">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Officiis, optio eveniet? Impedit nesciunt, natus facilis eveniet itaque harum exercitationem quam perferendis. Illo, dignissimos esse quia eveniet assumenda debitis dolore deleniti.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>